videos.description: Herbert Jones catches up to Ole Miss' Breein Tyree and swats his dunk attempt.
videos.headline: Jones skies for massive chase-down block

videos.description: Kira Lewis Jr. finds Donta Hall, who finishes with the slam.
videos.headline: Hall hammers wide-open slam

videos.description: Terence Davis breaks the tie with a deep 3-pointer late, to give Ole Miss the lead.
videos.headline: Davis breaks tie with wide-open 3

videos.description: After Kira Lewis Jr. misses a layup, John Petty seals the win for Alabama with a putback dunk.
videos.headline: Petty smacks go-ahead putback dunk
